  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kafkaesque: The Nightmare Trial</strong> is a psychological survival horror game that thrusts you into a world of bureaucratic nightmares and existential dread.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136850/extras/f6b061ccb55556cef6bca2b3fda960b1.webp?t=1758678387\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve twisted puzzles, manage scarce resources, and battle monstrous manifestations of authority. Navigate a nightmarish bureaucracy as you piece together the dark truth behind your arrest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136850/extras/5ab1e472fe937e550b59ca6909ed6cc2.webp?t=1758678387\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll navigate a maze of early 20th century bureaucratic architecture while confronting corrupted officials like the cryptic Inspector and the ominous Magistrate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136850/extras/ef36ee0161290bd3ee1c0910af186a91.webp?t=1758678387\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel a conspiracy that reaches far beyond your case, challenging your perception of justice and reality itself. Your investigation leads to one of three distinct endings as you face the brutal truth of your fate and the corruption that plagues this world.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kafkaesque: The Nightmare Trial</strong> is a psychological survival horror game that thrusts you into a world of bureaucratic nightmares and existential dread.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136850/extras/f6b061ccb55556cef6bca2b3fda960b1.webp?t=1758678387\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve twisted puzzles, manage scarce resources, and battle monstrous manifestations of authority. Navigate a nightmarish bureaucracy as you piece together the dark truth behind your arrest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136850/extras/5ab1e472fe937e550b59ca6909ed6cc2.webp?t=1758678387\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll navigate a maze of early 20th century bureaucratic architecture while confronting corrupted officials like the cryptic Inspector and the ominous Magistrate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136850/extras/ef36ee0161290bd3ee1c0910af186a91.webp?t=1758678387\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel a conspiracy that reaches far beyond your case, challenging your perception of justice and reality itself. Your investigation leads to one of three distinct endings as you face the brutal truth of your fate and the corruption that plagues this world.</p>",
